<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-01-28T01:35:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-01-28T01:35:00-05:00" n="681" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d681">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">891.113/21: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Iran</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Schnare</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the
                                    <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Tehran</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-01-28T10:00:00+03:25">January
                                    28, 1943—10 a.m.</date>
                                <lb/> [Received 2:44 p.m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>99. My 58, January 18. Russian Ambassador says the contract for operation
                            of the arms plants with minor changes has been signed but that details
                            of payment for arms and ammunition have yet to be agreed on. Copy of
                            amendments will follow later.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Schnare</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>